&lt;p style="margin-bottom: 15px; font-style: italic;"&gt;Usually, a president’s cabinet represents the best he has to offer in terms of the team needed to run the government as effectively as possible. Usually. Obviously not in the current case, because perhaps choosing a team based on shared hobbies and phobias rather than on their professional abilities isn’t the best way to go about it… Don’t you think, Mr. President?&lt;/p&gt;
